洋基老爹说他要退休将一生奉献给耶稣https://www.nme.com/news/music/daddy-yankee-says-hes-retiring-to-devote-his-life-to-jesus-3555056?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=daddy-yankee-says-他退休将一生奉献给耶稣Tom SkinnerThu, 07 Dec 2023 07:51:28 +0000 Music NewsNewsReggaeton https://www.nme.com/?p=3555056 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洋基老爹在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “成功的生活并不等于有目标的生活”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daddy-yankee-says-hes-retiring-to-devote-his-life-to-jesus-3555056">《洋基老爹说他将退休并将一生奉献给耶稣》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洋基老爹在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daddy-yankee">洋基老爹</a>表示，他将退出音乐界，将一生奉献给耶稣。</p><p>据<a href="https://people.com/daddy-yankee-retiring-to-devote-life-to-christianity-8411537" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>报道，这位说唱歌手和雷鬼艺术家最近在波多黎各圣胡安的 Coliseo José Miguel Agrelot 竞技场的舞台上谈到了他的计划。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/ozuna-anuel-aa-los-dioses-cardi-b-latin-music-best-in-world-2871822">波多黎各流行偶像奥祖纳：“拉丁音乐是世界上最好的音乐！”</a></strong></li></ul><p> “我的朋友们，这是我一生中最重要的一天。我想分享它......因为成功的生活与有目标的生活不同，”他在最后一场音乐会上告诉观众（翻译自西班牙语）。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C0a5YMJgfGz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><p></p><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display: block; height: 50px; margin: 0 auto 12px; width: 50px;"></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"><div style="color: #3897f0; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 550; line-height: 18px;">在 Instagram 上查看这篇文章</div></div><div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"><div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(7px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: 8px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style="width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p> <a style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C0a5YMJgfGz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">洋基老爹 (@daddyyankee) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p>这位“加索里纳”明星接着解释说，尽管他在音乐上取得了成功，但他感到生活中一片空白，只有当他开始更多地关注自己的信仰时，他才能填补这种空白。</p><p> “这就是为什么今晚我承认耶稣为我而活——我也会为他而活，”他继续说道。 “我拥有的所有工具——比如音乐、社交媒体、我的平台、麦克风，上帝给我的一切现在都是为了他。”</p><p>扬基的真名是拉蒙·罗德里格斯，他总结道：“我是人类，每个追随我的人都应该追随耶稣基督。”随后，他在社交媒体上分享了一段演讲视频，视频最后燃放了十字架烟花，并附上文字：“基督爱你”（西班牙语）。</p><p>这位艺术家于 2022 年宣布，他的专辑《Legendaddy》将是他的最后一张专辑，同时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daddy-yankee-announces-final-album-and-farewell-tour-3186757">确认他将退出音乐界并进行告别巡演</a>。</p><p>罗德里格斯当时用西班牙语（由<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-latin/daddy-yankee-retiring-last-album-1324403/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>翻译）说道：“这个职业生涯就像一场马拉松。我终于看到了最终目标。现在我要和大家一起享受你们给予我的一切。</p><p> “人们说我让这个流派走向了全球，但是你给了我打开大门并使这个流派成为世界上最大的流派的钥匙。”</p><p>他补充道：“在我们长大的贫民区，我们大多数人都想成为毒贩。今天，我去了巴里奥斯，大多数人都想成为艺术家，这对我来说意义重大。”</p><p> Daddy Yankee 凭借 2017 年与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-bieber">Justin Bieber</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/luis-fonsi">Luis Fonsi</a>合作的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/despacito-now-streamed-song-ever-2113022">《Despacito (Remix)》</a>赢得了英国排行榜冠军。根据<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/17167/daddy-yankee/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>官方排行榜</em></a>，该赛道在榜首的时间长达 11 周。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daddy-yankee-says-hes-retiring-to-devote-his-life-to-jesus-3555056">《洋基老爹说他将退休并将一生奉献给耶稣》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
凯西·威尔逊表示蒂姆·艾伦在《圣诞老人》片场“太他妈的粗鲁了” https://www.nme.com/news/tv/casey-wilson-says-tim-allen-was-so-fucking-rude-on-the-santa-clauses-set-3555023?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=凯西·威尔逊说蒂姆·艾伦在圣诞老人套装上太他妈粗鲁了Surej SinghThu, 07 Dec 2023 06:24:20 +0000 NewsTV NewsDisney https://www.nme.com/?p=3555023 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯西·威尔逊、蒂姆·艾伦。图片来源：Jon Kopaloff/Getty Images 和 Michael Kovac/Getty Images" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这确实是我与联合主演经历过的最糟糕的经历”</p><p>凯西<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/casey-wilson-says-tim-allen-was-so-fucking-rude-on-the-santa-clauses-set-3555023">·威尔逊 (Casey Wilson) 称蒂姆·艾伦 (Tim Allen) 在“圣诞老人”片场“太粗鲁了”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯西·威尔逊、蒂姆·艾伦。图片来源：Jon Kopaloff/Getty Images 和 Michael Kovac/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/casey-wilson-tim-allen@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>女演员凯西·威尔逊详细介绍了她与蒂姆·艾伦在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">迪士尼+</a>系列剧<em>《圣诞老人》</em>片场合作的经历，称他“太他妈的粗鲁了”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/best-christmas-movies-of-all-time-3370745">史上 50 部最佳圣诞电影</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/tim-allen-rude-set-behavior-santa-clauses-casey-wilson-1235824808/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道，凯西·威尔逊 (Casey Wilson) 在她的<a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/0tbbgpo7tpCYoLEIxBlgYI?si=455463aa76034342" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Bitch Sesh</em>播客</a>的最新一集节目中公开反对蒂姆·艾伦 (Tim Allen) 在<em>迪士尼</em>圣诞系列片场的行为，她说她一直对此保持沉默，因为节目中的制片人是“一位伟大的制片人”。她的朋友”，因为她的孩子“喜欢电影”。</p><p> “蒂姆·艾伦真是个混蛋。这确实是我与联合主演经历过的最糟糕的经历，”她说。她接着回忆起一个场景，其中她本应将圣诞老人误认为是入侵者，从而阐述了自己的观点。 </p><figure id="attachment_3555050" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3555050" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3555050" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause@2000x1270.jpg" alt="1994 年电影《圣诞老人》中的场景中，蒂姆·艾伦手里拿着一个洋娃娃站在圣诞树旁。（摄影：华特迪士尼影业/盖蒂图片社）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3555050" class="wp-caption-text">蒂姆·艾伦 (Tim Allen) 1994 年主演的电影《圣诞老人》。图片来源：华特迪士尼影业/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>威尔逊回忆道：“所以我就在一个场景中。只有我和蒂姆·艾伦，我应该向他扔东西。我认为他是一个窃贼。所以他从烟囱里下来，显然是圣诞老人，我醒来时以为有入侵者，基本上就像入室盗窃的场景。所以我就向他扔东西。”</p><p>她继续说：“[他]走到离我四英尺远的制片人身边，然后我听到了他的声音，他说，‘你必须告诉她不要再踩我的台词了。’”制片人满脸惊恐地转向我，不得不一只脚走到我面前，他说道，‘嗯，蒂姆会要求你停止踩他的台词。’”</p><p>威尔逊接着说，当艾伦在片场时，每个人都“如履薄冰”。 “当他完成后，他真是太粗鲁了。从来没有眼神交流，从来没有说过任何话。太不舒服了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3555051" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3555051" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3555051" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause-02@2000x1270.jpg" alt="蒂姆·艾伦 (Tim Allen) 1994 年主演的电影《圣诞老人》。图片来源：华特迪士尼影业/盖蒂图片社" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause-02@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause-02@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause-02@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause-02@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause-02@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tim-allen-santa-clause-02@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3555051" class="wp-caption-text">蒂姆·艾伦 (Tim Allen) 1994 年主演的电影《圣诞老人》。图片来源：华特迪士尼影业/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>据威尔逊说，有一次艾伦在拍摄中途离开片场而没有通知任何人，这导致威尔逊与他的替身相对应。这位女演员还透露，剧组中有人告诉她，她“在美好的一天见到了[艾伦]”。</p><p>蒂姆·艾伦尚未对威尔逊的说法做出回应。</p><p> <em>《圣诞老人》</em>是迪士尼+系列剧，是艾伦圣诞电影三部曲<em>《圣诞老人》</em> （1994 年）、 <em>《圣诞老人 2》</em> （2002 年）和<em>《圣诞老人 3：逃脱条款》</em> （2006 年）的续集。</p><p>最近，蒂姆·艾伦向吉米·法伦透露，迪士尼已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/tim-allen-tom-hanks-approached-toy-story-5-3547618">与他和汤姆·汉克斯联系拍摄第五部<em>《玩具总动员》</em>电影</a>。</p><p>凯西<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/casey-wilson-says-tim-allen-was-so-fucking-rude-on-the-santa-clauses-set-3555023">·威尔逊 (Casey Wilson) 称蒂姆·艾伦 (Tim Allen) 在“圣诞老人”片场“太粗鲁了”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
